        <abstract> 
<p>CD proposes setting price [of <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>] on a printing of 1000 copies, but to have 250 additional copies printed – with CD paying for paper and press work. JM would not repay CD until 1000 are sold; and profits on the 250 to be divided as usual. CD proposes this because he does not think a second edition will ever be needed.</p> 
        </abstract>
